cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.GT, cs.PL 

This paper is about general game playing (GGP) and inductive general game playing (IGGP), which are topics related to artificial intelligence (AI) and machine learning (ML). Therefore, cs.AI and cs.LG are the most likely categories. The paper also discusses the use of logic programming (LP) and ILP, which are related to computational linguistics (CL) and programming languages (PL), respectively. Therefore, cs.CL and cs.PL are also likely categories. Finally, the paper involves game theory (GT) as it discusses the GGP competition and the evaluation of agents' performance.
